section.section:
In this subsection, "Identification number" means the identifying number:
On the purchaser's driver's license;
If the purchaser is a resident of the State, on the purchaser's identification card as provided for in the Transportation Article;
If the purchaser is not a resident of the State, on the purchaser's identification card that is issued by the purchaser's home state or jurisdiction; or
The identification number on a United States military identification card.
